snippet.title: Create Your Rockstar Brand with Amber Griffiths
snippet.description:
http://EliteOnlinePublishing.com Jenn Foster and Melanie Johnson speak with Amber Griffiths about how to create a rockstar brand. Amber is a Speaker and Brand Strategist. She is the CEO of Your Brand by Design and absolutely LOVES what she does. Amber Brands entrepreneurs to stand out as leaders and own their market, creating a ripple effect of increased joy and profits.

Video URL: https://youtu.be/MX72VjZEAJ0
Website: http://EliteOnlinePublishing.com
http://www.yourbrandbydesign.com/
